<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>OrbitBot - Explore the Universe</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600;800&display=swap');

        :root {
            --primary: #5865F2;
            --accent: #00d2ff;
            --bg: #09090b;
            --card-bg: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            color: #fff;
            margin: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            background-image: 
                radial-gradient(circle at 15% 50%, rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%),
                radial-gradient(circle at 85% 30%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%);
        }

        /* Navigation */
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 20px 50px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            position: fixed;
            width: calc(100% - 100px);
            top: 0;
            z-index: 100;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
        }

        .logo {
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            letter-spacing: -1px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .logo i { color: var(--primary); }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #aaa;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 500;
            position: relative;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover { color: #fff; }

        .nav-links a::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 0;
            height: 2px;
            bottom: -5px;
            left: 0;
            background-color: var(--primary);
            transition: width 0.3s ease;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover::after { width: 100%; }

        .btn-login {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            padding: 8px 20px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            transition: 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-login:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); }

        /* Hero Section */
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
            animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 5rem;
            line-height: 1;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff 0%, #aaa 100%);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            animation: slideUp 0.8s ease-out;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #888;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            animation: slideUp 1s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-btn {
            padding: 18px 40px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 50px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px -10px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.5);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            animation: bounceIn 1.2s ease-out;
        }

        .hero-btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px) scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px -10px rgba(88, 101, 242, 0.6);
        }

        /* Features Cards */
        .features {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 30px;
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: -100px auto 100px;
            padding: 0 20px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 10;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--card-bg);
            border: 1px solid var(--glass-border);
            backdrop-filter: blur(20px);
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 24px;
            transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
            cursor: default;
        }

        .card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.06);
            border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }

        .card-icon {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: var(--accent);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1);
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            border-radius: 16px;
            transition: 0.4s;
        }

        .card:hover .card-icon {
            background: var(--accent);
            color: #000;
            transform: rotate(10deg);
        }

        .card h3 { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 1.5rem; }
        .card p { color: #888; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0; }

        /* Animations */
        @keyframes fadeIn { from { opacity: 0; } to { opacity: 1; } }
        @keyframes slideUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(30px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
        @keyframes bounceIn { 
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0.3); } 
            50% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1.05); } 
            70% { transform: scale(0.9); } 
            100% { transform: scale(1); } 
        }

        /* Responsive */
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            nav { padding: 20px; width: calc(100% - 40px); }
            .nav-links { display: none; }
            .features { margin-top: 0; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <nav>
        <div class="logo"><i class="fa-solid fa-user-astronaut"></i> OrbitBot</div>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="#">Home</a>
            <a href="#features">Features</a>
            <a href="#">Commands</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/orbitbot">GitHub</a>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <section class="hero">
        <h1>Explore the Cosmos<br>From Discord.</h1>
        <p>Track the ISS in real-time, discover detailed planet information, and get daily astronomy updates. Your personal space assistant is here.</p>
        <a href="https://discord.com/api/oauth2/authorize?client_id=<%= clientId %>&permissions=8&scope=bot%20applications.commands" class="hero-btn">
            <i class="fa-brands fa-discord"></i> Add to Discord
        </a>
    </section>

    <section class="features" id="features">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-satellite"></i></div>
            <h3>ISS Tracking</h3>
            <p>Get real-time coordinates and mapping of the International Space Station instantly.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-globe"></i></div>
            <h3>Planet Encyclopedia</h3>
            <p>Access detailed data about every planet in our solar system, sourced from NASA APIs.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon"><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i></div>
            <h3>Astronomy Picture</h3>
            <p>Start your day with the Astronomy Picture of the Day (APOD) directly in your server.</p>
                </div>
            </section>
        
            <footer style="text-align: center; padding: 40px 20px; color: #666; border-top: 1px solid var(--glass-border); margin-top: 50px;">
                <p>&copy; 2025 OrbitBot. All rights reserved.</p>
                <div style="margin-top: 10px;">
                    <a href="/tos" style="color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; transition: color 0.2s;">Terms of Service</a>
                    <a href="/privacy" style="color: #888; text-decoration: none; margin: 0 10px; transition: color 0.2s;">Privacy Policy</a>
                </div>
            </footer>
        
        </body>
        </html>
        